text: Louis-Henry Lemirre was an archer from France. He was born on 8 April 1929 and died on 1 August 2000. Lemirre competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics.Louis- Henry LemirreLouis Henri LEMIRRE == References == Category:1929 births Category:2000 deaths Category:French archers Category:Olympians for France Category:People from Calvados Category:Sportspeople from Normandy
